<tab>Archimagicians are great magicians who contempt brute force. Those who have become famous as warriors and achieved a serius title can forget about the guild of Archimagicians. Guild members have no military skillsěč, which is compensated by their excellent knowledge of the magic of elements. However, this dosen't mean an archimagician cannot stand up for himself in battle - the guild's secret knowledge provides serious protection from physical attacks.<br>
